  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><p>1. JOB DESCRIPTION</p><p>Job Title</p><p>Prime Mover Driver</p><p>Occupation</p><p>Driver</p><p>Job Description & Requirements</p><p><strong>Responsibilities & Requirements</strong></p><p>. To drive & operate prime mover safely & proficiently within PSA's container Terminals</p><p>. To transport containerised cargoes to designated locations in Singapore</p><p>. Must have valid class 4 license</p><p>. Able to drive with a towed trailer up to 40 footer on the road</p><p>. Willing to work on early morning shifts</p><p>. Willing to work on weekends</p><p>. Willing to work OT when required</p><p>. Experience not required, as training is provided</p><p>. Able to start work immediately will be an advantage</p><p><strong>Attractive Salary Package</strong></p><p>Salary Range: $4,000 to $5,000</p><p>Full CPF contribution</p><p><u><strong>Benefits</strong></u></p><p>Shifts allowance</p><p>Weekend allowance</p><p>Year End Bonus</p>",
